description: Demolition of Lok'N Store building and erection of two 6-8 storey buildings for residential use - 124 flats (43x1 bedroom; 75x2 bed. and 6x3 bed. flats), including 46 affordable housing units (30 for rent and 16 intermediate) (37%) and use for a GP Doctors surgery (715sqm); basement parking for 104 cars and cycle parking with access from Skerne Road.
